values:
Great day... yea... outstanding! Oh, thats right I stepped on a FUCKING NAIL! Yup straight into my heal... touched bone i believe. Tomorrow i get to get my tetnus shot... It hurts just keeping it still. I hope it doesn't stay like this, the pain and irri-fuckin-tation, to long. Other than that outstanding event im ok and missin that one person who brings me calm and peace. Love you!


         -Nick-

I don't have much to say... that's a first. I got done the doctors and will be starting up my meds soon, but that depends on a few things first. My "doctor" is ok... better than the last 3 I had. This will only last until its time to move, but thats 2 months so i got plenty of time. Art is still looking like crap, but i guess its coming along. The anatomy of the human body is pretty interesting. The one thing i need to work on is the shadowing a bit more. The form of the bodies are perfect but the shadowing is the only thing holding back the realistic look. Mumble mumble mumble... I talk to myself enough through the day to fill a book worth of info and now im recording my thoughts... weak. 

                                                              -Nick-
